	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">bazz wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">why not just do nibble &lt;&lt; (range-1) in that case.</div><br />Because some languages leave SHL by a negative number <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Undefined_behavior" class="postlink">undefined</a>, and others raise an exception when it occurs.

		

